import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Paper,
  Button,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemText,
  Chip,
} from '@mui/material';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';
import {
  School,
  Engineering,
  Computer,
  Public,
  People,
  TrendingUp,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const StyledCard = styled(Card)(({ theme }) => ({
  height: '100%',
  display: 'flex',
  flexDirection: 'column',
  transition: 'transform 0.2s',
  '&:hover': {
    transform: 'scale(1.02)',
  },
}));

const StatCard = ({ title, value, description, icon: Icon }) => (
  <StyledCard elevation={3}>
    <CardContent>
      <Box display="flex" alignItems="center" mb={2}>
        <Icon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: 'primary.main', mr: 2 }} />
        <Typography variant="h4" component="div" color="primary">
          {value}
        </Typography>
      </Box>
      <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
        {title}
      </Typography>
      <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
        {description}
      </Typography>
    </CardContent>
  </StyledCard>
);

const Home = () => {
  const stats = [
    {
      title: "TOPPERS' TOP CHOICE",
      value: "15th",
      description: "POSITION IN TAMILNADU TNEA 2024 ADMISSIONS",
      icon: TrendingUp,
    },
    {
      title: "COIMBATORE RANK",
      value: "7th",
      description: "IN COIMBATORE TNEA 2024 ADMISSIONS",
      icon: School,
    },
    {
      title: "GLOBAL SCIENTISTS",
      value: "TOP 2%",
      description: "SCIENTISTS OF THE WORLD WITH SRI ESHWAR",
      icon: Engineering,
    },
    {
      title: "GLOBAL PARTNERSHIPS",
      value: "50+",
      description: "PARTNERSHIPS WITH UNIVERSITIES AROUND THE WORLD",
      icon: Public,
    },
  ];

  return (
    <Box>
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Box
        sx={{
          bgcolor: 'primary.main',
          color: 'white',
          py: 8,
          textAlign: 'center',
        }}
      >
        <Container>
          <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom>
            Sri Eshwar Engineering College
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
            Best Engineering College in Tamil Nadu
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="subtitle1">
            Achieve academic excellence, innovative research, and career success
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Stats Section */}
      <Container sx={{ my: 8 }}>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          {stats.map((stat, index) => (
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3} key={index}>
              <StatCard {...stat} />
            </Grid>
          ))}
        </Grid>
      </Container>

      {/* Academic Programs */}
      <Box sx={{ bgcolor: 'grey.100', py: 8 }}>
        <Container>
          <Typography variant="h3" textAlign="center" gutterBottom>
            ACADEMICS @ SRI ESHWAR
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={4} mt={2}>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <StyledCard>
                <CardContent>
                  <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                    UG Programmes
                  </Typography>
                  <List>
                    <ListItem>
                      <ListItemText primary="B.E. Computer Science and Engineering" />
                    </ListItem>
                    <ListItem>
                      <ListItemText primary="B.E. Mechanical Engineering" />
                    </ListItem>
                    <ListItem>
                      <ListItemText primary="B.E. Electronics and Communication" />
                    </ListItem>
                  </List>
                </CardContent>
              </StyledCard>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <StyledCard>
                <CardContent>
                  <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                    PG Programmes
                  </Typography>
                  <List>
                    <ListItem>
                      <ListItemText primary="M.E. Computer Science and Engineering" />
                    </ListItem>
                    <ListItem>
                      <ListItemText primary="M.E. Manufacturing Engineering" />
                    </ListItem>
                  </List>
                </CardContent>
              </StyledCard>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <StyledCard>
                <CardContent>
                  <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                    Research
                  </Typography>
                  <List>
                    <ListItem>
                      <ListItemText primary="Ph.D. Programs" />
                    </ListItem>
                    <ListItem>
                      <ListItemText primary="Research Centers" />
                    </ListItem>
                    <ListItem>
                      <ListItemText primary="Publications" />
                    </ListItem>
                  </List>
                </CardContent>
              </StyledCard>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Campus Life */}
      <Container sx={{ my: 8 }}>
        <Typography variant="h3" textAlign="center" gutterBottom>
          CAMPUS LIFE
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={4} mt={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <StyledCard>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                  World-Class Facilities
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemText primary="State-of-the-art Labs" />
                  </ListItem>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemText primary="Modern Library" />
                  </ListItem>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemText primary="Sports Complex" />
                  </ListItem>
                </List>
              </CardContent>
            </StyledCard>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <StyledCard>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                  Student Activities
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemText primary="Technical Clubs" />
                  </ListItem>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemText primary="Cultural Events" />
                  </ListItem>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemText primary="Sports Teams" />
                  </ListItem>
                </List>
              </CardContent>
            </StyledCard>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Home;
